---

<section id="testimonials" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-24 h-24 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-white/10 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
        </svg>
        Testimoni Pelanggan
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Apa Kata <span class="text-primary-200">Pelanggan Kami</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Lihat bagaimana perkhidmatan kami telah membantu perniagaan lain mencapai kejayaan dalam talian.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
        <div class="group bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-300 to-primary-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-800 font-bold text-xl mr-4">
              A
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Puan Aisyah</h4>
              <p class="text-primary-200 text-sm">Usahawan Makanan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <svg class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-8 h-8 text-primary-300 opacity-50" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed relative z-10 pl-6">
              Sangat puas hati! Website siap cepat, cantik dan saya tak perlu keluar duit awal. Proses tempahan pun sangat mudah dan team sangat membantu.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="group bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-300 to-secondary-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary-800 font-bold text-xl mr-4">
              F
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Encik Faizal</h4>
              <p class="text-primary-200 text-sm">Pemilik Kedai Online</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <svg class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-8 h-8 text-primary-300 opacity-50" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed relative z-10 pl-6">
              Mudah, cepat dan mesra bajet. Sangat disyorkan untuk bisnes kecil. Pelanggan saya juga senang untuk hubungi saya melalui website.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
        <div class="group bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-300 to-accent-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-accent-800 font-bold text-xl mr-4">
              N
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Puan Nurul</h4>
              <p class="text-primary-200 text-sm">Pemilik Butik</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <svg class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-8 h-8 text-primary-300 opacity-50" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed relative z-10 pl-6">
              Design yang diberikan sangat profesional, melebihi jangkaan saya. Perkhidmatan yang berbaloi dengan harga yang ditawarkan.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Testimonial 4 -->
        <div class="group bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/15 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-300 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-green-800 font-bold text-xl mr-4">
              Z
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Encik Zulkifli</h4>
              <p class="text-primary-200 text-sm">Pengerusi NGO</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <svg class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-8 h-8 text-primary-300 opacity-50" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h4v10h-10z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed relative z-10 pl-6">
              Sebagai NGO, kami sangat menghargai perkhidmatan yang berpatutan. Website kami kini lebih profesional dan mudah untuk dikemaskini.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16 pt-16 border-t border-white/20">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">100+</div>
          <div class="text-primary-200">Pelanggan Puas Hati</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">98%</div>
          <div class="text-primary-200">Rating Kepuasan</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">3-5</div>
          <div class="text-primary-200">Hari Siap</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">24/7</div>
          <div class="text-primary-200">Sokongan</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>